(4551, 30, '_yoast_wpseo_twitter-description', 'Leo Club of University of Moratuwa is one of the best clubs in Leo District 306 A2 Sri Lanka from its inception. Set of undergraduates from University of Moratuwa, who were fed up with their regular academic work looking for a change formed the club in early 2003.'),
