(4558, 1273, '_yoast_wpseo_metadesc', 'Leo Lion Pramod Sean Wimalatunga is the leader of the Leo Multiple District 306 for the fiscal year 2017/2018 under the slogan “Lead the Humanity”.  Leo Pramod Wimalatunga is a proud product of Leo District 306A2 who lead the District 306A2 on leoistic year 2015/2016. He got his secondary education Isipathana College, Colombo-05, and joined Leo club of Rattanapitiya in 2009.'),
