(572, 2, '2017-10-24 15:00:40', '2017-10-24 09:30:40', 'A Comedy-drama directed by Mr Sarath Kothalawala \"Eka Sakkuwe\" will unveil,\n*on 25th of October 2017\n*at Old Gymnasium of University of Moratuwa\n*Show times : 4.30pm and 7.30 pm\n*Tickets: Rs. 200, 300, 500\n\nWell recognized actors Saranga Disasekara, Pubudu Chathuranga, Sarath Chandrasiri, Kumudu Nishantha, Nishantha Pieris, W. Dombagahawatta perform in the play.\n\nOrganized by: Leo club of University of Moratuwa\nFor More Info (\"ඒකා සාක්කුවේ\" Official Facebook Page):<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Eka-Sakkuwe-1658725344366082/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.facebook.com/<wbr />Eka-Sakkuwe-165872534436608<wbr />2/</a>\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t1px1Fkg9Q0[/embedyt]\n\n\"ඒකා සාක්කුවේ කිව්වම...අපි දැන හෝ නොදැන සමාජයේ ඉන්න හැම කෙනෙක්ම ඉන්නේ කාගේ හරි සාක්කුවක....අපි ඉන්නේ මොන සාක්කුවේද කියලා බලන්න පුළුවන් එදාට ඒකා සාක්කුවේ බැලුවාම.....\"\n- ඒකා සාක්කුවේ රංගන ශිල්පී සරත් චන්ද්‍රසිරි\nඔක්:25 | OLD GYM | 4.30 P.M | 7.00 P.M\n<a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/ekasakkuwe?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=10155320610573369\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\"><span class=\"_5afx\"><span class=\"_58cl _5afz\" aria-label=\"hashtag\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">EkaSakkuwe</span></span></a> <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/stagedrama?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=10155320610573369\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\"><span class=\"_5afx\"><span class=\"_58cl _5afz\" aria-label=\"hashtag\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">StageDrama</span></span></a> <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/uomleos?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=10155320610573369\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\"><span class=\"_5afx\"><span class=\"_58cl _5afz\" aria-label=\"hashtag\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">UomLeos</span></span></a> <a class=\"_58c