(585, 2, '2017-10-24 15:01:12', '2017-10-24 09:31:12', 'A Comedy-drama directed by Mr Sarath Kothalawala \"Eka Sakkuwe\" will unveil,\r\n*on 25th of October 2017\r\n*at Old Gymnasium of University of Moratuwa\r\n*Show times : 4.30pm and 7.30 pm\r\n*Tickets: Rs. 200, 300, 500\r\n\r\nWell recognized actors Saranga Disasekara, Pubudu Chathuranga, Sarath Chandrasiri, Kumudu Nishantha, Nishantha Pieris, W. Dombagahawatta perform in the play.\r\n\r\nOrganized by: Leo club of University of Moratuwa\r\nFor More Info (\"ඒකා සාක්කුවේ\" Official Facebook Page):<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Eka-Sakkuwe-1658725344366082/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.facebook.com/<wbr />Eka-Sakkuwe-165872534436608<wbr />2/</a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=66Lth46Egbg[/embedyt]\r\n\r\nකවුරු කොහොම කිව්වත් අපි හැමෝම ඉන්නේ කාගෙහරි සාක්කුවක... එන්න ඒ සාක්කුව මොකක්ද කියලා දැනගන්න..... ඒකා සාක්කුවේ ඔක්:25 | OLD GYM | 4.30 P.M | 7.00 P.M. <a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%23EkaSakkuwe\">#EkaSakkuwe</a> <a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%23StageDrama\">#StageDrama</a> <a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%23UomLeos\">#UomLeos</a> <a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%23fundraiser\">#fundraiser</a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t1px1Fkg9Q0[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n\"ඒකා සාක්කුවේ කිව්වම...අපි දැන හෝ නොදැන සමාජයේ ඉන්න හැම කෙනෙක්ම ඉන්නේ කාගේ හරි සාක්කුවක....අපි ඉන්නේ මොන සාක්කුවේද කියලා බලන්න පුළුවන් එදාට ඒකා සාක්කුවේ බැලුවාම.....\"\r\n- ඒකා සාක්කුවේ රංගන ශිල්පී සරත් චන්ද්‍රසිරි\r\nඔක්:25 | OLD GYM | 4.30 P.M | 7.00 P.M\r\n<a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/ekasakkuwe?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=101553