(858, 2, '2017-11-11 22:53:14', '2017-11-11 17:23:14', 'It’s the time to give a helping hand to the people who deserve it the most, add a value to the name of humanity, bring a smile on an innocent face and show them the way to live a better life than today.\r\nThe third phase of the Service Project Series,” Hadagasma” , done by the Leo Club of University of Moratuwa, will be happening on the days of 18th and 19th of November, aiming the people in Kellagama area. The project will go under several steps including the following progr<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">ams.\r\n*Education with humanity (@ Kallagama Navodya Vidyalaya)\r\n*Knowing about Diabetes (@Kellagama)\r\n*Knowing about Cancer (@Kellagama)\r\n*Leadership and Mortivation (@ Kallagama Navodya Vidyalaya)</span>\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n\r\nJoin your hands with us and help to enhance someone’s life to a better future.\r\n<a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/hadagasma?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=10155370372213369\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\"><span class=\"_5afx\"><span class=\"_58cl _5afz\" aria-label=\"hashtag\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">hadagasma</span></span></a> <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/uomleos?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=10155370372213369\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\"><span class=\"_5afx\"><span class=\"_58cl _5afz\" aria-label=\"hashtag\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">uomleos</span></span></a> <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/cheers?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=10155370372213369\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\"><span class=\"_5afx\"><span class=\"_58cl _5afz\" aria-label=\"hashtag\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">cheers</span></span></a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-860 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/23517826_10155371899743369_2504407571279829812_n-300x179.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"317\" />\r\n<div id=\"id_5a0731cde5cb18734850389\" class=\"text_exposed_root text_exposed\">“The best way to predict your future is to create it”\r\n-Abraham Lincoln-\r\nIt’s our aim to give them a little helping hand to come up, from the name of education and create their own future. The better they learn, more fruitful their future lives would be. That is why the first step of the project series Hadagesma - Kallagama became a seminar on mathematics, going with the t<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">heme, \'Education with Humanity\'. It will be happening on the days of 18th and 19th of November, aiming the O/L students in Kaallagama Navodya Vidyalaya with the aim of polishing their mathematics skills and helping them on the upcoming O/L examination. It is an effort to make them feel the essence of education. Be there and join with us, to help someone on their education.\r\n<a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/hadagasma\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\">#hadagasma</a> <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/phase3\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\">#phase3</a> <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/uomleos\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\">#uomleos</a> <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/cheers\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\">#cheers</a></span></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>', 'හදගැස්ම - Heartbeat | කෑල්ලගම', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '%e0%b7%84%e0%b6%af%e0%b6%9c%e0%b7%90%e0%b7%83%e0%b7%8a%e0%b6%b8-%e0%b6%9a%e0%b7%91%e0%b6%bd%e0%b7%8a%e0%b6%bd%e0%b6%9c%e0%b6%b8', '', '', '2017-11-12 20:33:06', '2017-11-12 15:03:06', '', 0, 'http://www.uomleos.org/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=858', 0, 'tribe_events', '', 0),
