(969, 2, '2017-11-24 11:09:53', '2017-11-24 05:39:53', '<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The world of the preschooler is one of imagination and magic. Normally, children’s creativity will reach its peak before the age of six. During this period, kids tend to explore and learn about everything. Therefore, it is a critical time in the development of kids and parent and adults play a central role in it.</p>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-970\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/22310537_10155292248023369_159601343570130326_n-1-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" />\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We, the UoM leos, in line with the spirit of children’s day, conducted an art competition “Singithi sith ru”,  for the kids of Sumudu Preschool on the 04<sup>th</sup> October 2017 from 9.00am onwards. Kids are asked to draw paintings on that day. While they are drawing, we shared their fresh ideas in a friendly manner. We are able to refresh them by giving yoghurt also. Finally, kids were given with a present and wind up the session for the day.</p>\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-971 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/DSC_0236-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" />', 'සිඟිති සිත් රූ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e0%b7%83%e0%b7%92%e0%b6%9f%e0%b7%92%e0%b6%ad%e0%b7%92-%e0%b7%83%e0%b7%92%e0%b6%ad%e0%b7%8a-%e0%b6%bb%e0%b7%96', '', '', '2017-11-24 11:09:53', '2017-11-24 05:39:53', '', 0, 'http://www.uomleos.org/?p=969', 0, 'post', '', 0),
