n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSince then the Leo club of UOM remains the most outstanding club in the district, number of awards we achieved in 2nd district conference was 18 that was the result of the leadership provided by Leo Buddhi Hettiarachchi in Leostic year 2006/2007. In leoistic year 2007/2008 under the presidency of Leo Namal Karunarathne the club was again awarded as the Most outstanding Leo club in the Leo district 306A2 at the 3rd annual district conference. We achieved 12 project awards 7 individual awards and 2 district and club awards.\r\n\r\nLeo Buddhi Isurujith is the president of the Leo Club of University of Moratuwa for the Leoistic year 2017/18. The current membership of the club is about 89 members.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_62\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"300\"]<img class=\"wp-image-62 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/07-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /> Current President : Leo Budhdhi Isurujith[/caption]\r\n\r\nFrom the beginning, Leo Club of University of Moratuwa has been actively involving in community service projects and also enhancing leadership skills of university students . In the district Conference of 306A2, Leo Club of University of Moratuwa was the first runner up for the most outstanding Leo club of the district. Leo Club of University of Moratuwa also won the Most Outstanding University Leo Club in Sri Lanka in the Leo Multiple District conference and rewarded as the winners in Youth Leadership and Empowerment project, project on spotlight on Children, Multi Service project and project on Public Relationship, Communication and Marketing. Most importantly Leo Club of University of Moratuwa remains as one of the best and active student societies in the university where, lot of youngsters are gathered to serve the community are gathered to serve the community.', 'UoM Leos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1104-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-22 22:01:06', '2017-12-22 16:31:06', '', 1104, 'http://www.uomleos.org/2017/12/22/1104-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
