(1192, 2, '2017-12-24 13:30:38', '2017-12-24 08:00:38', 'As responsible citizens, developing and repairing religious places is one of our major responsibility. Because, they are the places where people can develop their spiritual life. According to the Buddhism, It is a great merit.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1195 size-full\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"952\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\nDamithu saviya is another community service project organized by UOM Leos taking hands with Leo club of Dehiwala North.It was held on 2<sup>nd</sup> November at Sudharmarama Viharaya, Hapugala. Pipeline system and the electricity system of the newly constructed lavatory was repaired with the help of Leos and prospects. Finally, we were able to conclude this project as another great effort taken by UOM Leos to develop and empower the religious places.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-1194 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-300x193.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" /> <img class=\"size-medium wp-image-1193 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-300x189.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"189\" />', 'දමිතු සවිය - Damithu Saviya', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e0%b6%af%e0%b6%b8%e0%b7%92%e0%b6%ad%e0%b7%94-%e0%b7%83%e0%b7%80%e0%b7%92%e0%b6%ba-damithu-saviya', '', '', '2017-12-24 13:41:16', '2017-12-24 08:11:16', '', 0, 'http://www.uomleos.org/?p=1192', 0, 'post', '', 0),
