(1196, 2, '2017-12-24 13:30:38', '2017-12-24 08:00:38', 'As responsible citizens, developing and repairing religious places is one of our major responsibility. Because, they are the places where people can develop their spiritual life. According to the Buddhism, It is a great merit.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1195 size-full\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"952\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\nDamithu saviya is another community service project organized by UOM Leos taking hands with Leo club of Dehiwala North.It was held on 2<sup>nd</sup> November at Sudharmarama Viharaya, Hapugala. Pipeline system and the electricity system of the newly constructed lavatory was repaired with the help of Leos and prospects. Finally, we were able to conclude this project as another great effort taken by UOM Leos to develop and empower the religious places.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-1194 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-300x193.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" /> <img class=\"size-medium wp-image-1193 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-300x189.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"189\" />', 'දමිතු සවිය - Damithu Saviya', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1192-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-24 13:30:38', '2017-12-24 08:00:38', '', 1192, 'http://www.uomleos.org/2017/12/24/1192-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1197, 2, '2017-12-24 13:33:48', '2017-12-24 08:03:48', '<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We, the UoM Leos correlate with the development of education sector of children in rural areas, with the intention of enhancing their mathematical and leadership skills. All what we desire is to show them how to dream big and give wings to those big dreams, from the name of education.</p>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1199 size-large\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-1-1024x567.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"415\" />\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This project series “Sihinayata Piyapath” was conducted continuously to encourage students who are going to sit for the G.C.E. O/L examination this year.</p>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1198 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-1-300x165.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"165\" />\r\n\r\nThe successful 8<sup>th</sup> phase of the project series was conducted on 3<sup>rd</sup> November at Thulhiriya Dharmasiri Senanayaka school, Kegalle. There, we discussed the mathematical problems targeting the G.C.E. Ordinary Level exam paper and taught them some easy ways to answer the questions while paying attention to each student as much as possible. This was carried out successfully throughout the day and we hope that our effort was a huge strength to them.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1200 size-large\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-1024x608.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"445\" />', 'Sihinayata Piyapath', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sihinayata-piyapath-2', '', '', '2017-12-24 13:40:23', '2017-12-24 08:10:23', '', 0, 'http://www.uomleos.org/?p=1197', 0, 'post', '', 0),
