(1288, 2, '2017-12-29 03:26:52', '2017-12-28 21:56:52', '{\n    \"hestia-pro::hestia_slider_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/cropped-1.jpg\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"LEO CLUB OF UNIVERSITY OF MORATUWA\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"&quot;Leadership - Experience - Opportunity&quot; We share as one family !!\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer-repeater-5a07eeadb6f14\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/2.jpg\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"LEO MASS INDUCTION 2017\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"LEO CLUB OF UNIVERSITY OF MORATUWA&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;&quot;Leadership - Experience - Opportunity&quot; We share as one family !!\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40a56\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/serve.jpg\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Take Your Responsibility\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"Do What You Can Do To The Society\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer-repeater-5a45673ab465e\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"}]\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 2,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2017-12-28 21:56:52\"\n    },\n    \"hestia-pro::hestia_features_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"[{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"fa-flag\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#00bcd4\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"We originated as the second university based leo club in Sri Lanka and the first in Leo district 306A2,on 23rd June 2003,Under the presidency of Leo Nadun Gunawardhana.So far we &#39;ve achieved a lot under many leaderships and guidance and still dedicate to continue the excellency.\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Origin\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40b56\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"fa-trophy\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#00bcd4\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"It&#39;s not all about awards,but our contribution and dedication was always appreciated. Most recently, we were rewarded with the title &quot;The Most Outstanding University Leo Club of Sri Lanka, Leostic Year 2016&#x2F;2017&quot; along with many other awards. The achievements and awards we gained so far are countless.They always remain with us as tokens of appriciation and models for motivation.\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Achievements\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40b66\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"fa-rocket\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#00bcd4\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"LEO - &#39; Leadership - Experience - Opportunity&#39;, we share as one family&#39;. While giving the priority to gain experience, we commit to do social services and help the people who needed it the most, in many perspectives. It&#39;s an effort to create the future leaders who feel people the most.&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Objective\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40b86\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"}]\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 2,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2017-12-28 21:50:53\"\n    },\n    \"hestia-pro::hestia_team_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"[{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"&quot; The home for nurturing creative, energetic, enthusiastic and courageous leaders, Leo club of university of Moratuwa &quot;&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;&lt;b&gt;- Lion Meena Wellala&lt;&#x2F;b&gt;\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/meena-300x300.jpg\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Leo Adviser\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer-repeater-59bd6116fc92a\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"&quot; Always be the change if you want to make a change. Be innovative and creative, then you can be the change easily. &lt;br &#x2F;&gt;Others will follow you and they will see the change you want to make. &quot;&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;&lt;b&gt;- Leo Buddhi Isurujith&lt;&#x2F;b&gt; \\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/07-300x300.jpg\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"President\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40c56\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"&quot; The world will be no doubltfully a better place if we don&#39;t miss our duties and responsibilities. &lt;br &#x2F;&gt;So, be a responsible one for both yourself and the society. &quot;&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;&lt;b&gt;- Leo Kasun Ramanayake&lt;&#x2F;b&gt;\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/19400108_1063772087087894_482606770736277013_n-e1501773580832-300x300.jpg\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Vice President\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40c66\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"&quot; The will for a good deed should come from bottom of the heart with no hidden intentions. That spiritual happiness gained through can never be stolen &amp; is priceless.&quot;&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;&lt;b&gt;- Leo Devini Shashiprabha&lt;&#x2F;b&gt;\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/12970830_1324238364259865_7600859878914646747_o-2-e1501773983304-300x300.jpg\