lly granted with the award of most outstanding Leo club, as many of former years, from PDP Leo Buddika Lakmal Gunasekara in the multiple conference held at defense school auditorium on July 2014.\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\r\n<strong>2015</strong></h3>\r\nAwarded as the Winner of the Leo district contest, for the excellence service provided towards the society and for the excessive support given to the Leo district 306, throughout the Leostic year 2014/2015, with the leadership of Leo Shehan Madushanka.\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\r\n<strong>2016</strong></h3>\r\nLeo Club of University of Moratuwa awarded as the most outstanding Leo club of the Leo Multiple district 306 – Sri Lanka, Under the Leadership of Leo Ivan Udakara from PMDP Leo Dumidu Jayakody.\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\r\n<strong>2017</strong></h3>\r\nUoM Leos were awarded for being the most outstanding University Leo club of the Leo Multiple district 306 – Sri Lanka, Under the Leadership of Leo Shehan Akmeemana, from PMDP Leo Rajitha Abeygunasekara.', 'Journey Towards Excellence', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1368-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-02 14:17:54', '2018-01-02 08:47:54', '', 1368, 'http://www.uomleos.org/2018/01/02/1368-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
