\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  <strong>2009</strong></h3>\r\nContinuing the Excellency, for the consecutive 4<sup>th</sup> time Most Outstanding Leo club of the Leo District 306 A2 was won by UoM Leos, at the yearend conference. Further, Leo Isuru Senadeera, an excellent leader produced by the club, was awarded as the Leo of the year for the Leostic year 2008/2009.\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" style=\"color: #0b93c4; font-size: 30px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  <strong>2011</strong></h3>\r\nFor the year 2011 Leo club of University of Moratuwa was awarded as the 2<sup>nd</sup> Runner up of the Leo District contest at the Leo District conference held at Hotel Galadari, under the leadership of Leo Damith Amarakon from PDP Leo Thilini Manamperi.\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" style=\"color: #0b93c4; font-size: 30px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  <strong>2012</strong></h3>\r\nUoM Leos were Lucky to produce first ever Leo District president to the Leo District 306 A2, from their own club in this year. And also they were blessed with the award of most outstanding Leo club of Leo Multiple district 306 – Sri Lanka, under the Leadership of Leo Naveen Thameera, from PMDP Leo Thiruparan Siwapathasudaram.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1403\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1403 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1st-ever-DP-300x207.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"276\" /> 1st 306 A2 District President From UoM Leos - 2012[/caption]\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" style=\"color: #0b93c4; font-size: 30px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  <strong>2013</strong></h3>\r\nLeo Club of University of Moratuwa Celebrated their 10<sup>th</sup> year anniversary, recalling their journey of pride and remarkable. In this year too, the award of Most Outstanding Leo Club, of the Leo district 306 A2, was in the hands of these lion cubs, under the leadership of Leo Chathuranga Gunasekara.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1404\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1404 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/10-any-300x207.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"276\" /> 10th Anniversary Celebration of UoM Leos - 2013[/caption]\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" style=\"color: #0b93c4; font-size: 30px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  <strong>2014</strong></h3>\r\nUnder the Leadership of Leo Ajith Ranaweera, UoM Leos were successfully granted with the award of most outstanding Leo club, as many of former years, from PDP Leo Buddika Lakmal Gunasekara in the multiple conference held at defense school auditorium on July 2014.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1405\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1405 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/multiple-conf-2014-300x207.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"276\" /> Awarded UoM Leos by Leo Multiple District - 2014[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1406\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1406 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/multiple-conf-2014_2-300x207.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"276\" /> UoM Leos representing the Leo Multiple District Conference - 2014[/caption]\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" style=\"color: #0b93c4; font-size: 30px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  <strong>2015</strong></h3>\r\nAwarded as the Winner of the Leo district contest, for the excellence service provided towards the society and for the excessive support given to the Leo district 306, throughout the Leostic year 2014/2015, with the leadership of Leo Shehan Madushanka.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1408\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1408 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/12th-Installation_2-300x207.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"276\" /> 12th Installation Ceremony - 2015[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1409\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1409 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/district-Conf_2015-300x207.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"276\" /> Leo District 306 A2 Conference - 2015[/caption]\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" style=\"color: #0b93c4; font-size: 30px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  <strong>2016</strong></h3>\r\nLeo Club of University of Moratuwa awarded as the most outstanding Leo club of the Leo Multiple district 306 – Sri Lanka, Under the Leadership of Leo Ivan Udakara from PMDP Leo Dumidu Jayakody.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1410\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1410 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/13-installation-300x207.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"276\" /> 13th Installation Ceremony - 2016[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1413\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1413 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/13612356_10153973841263369_1070856138815435737_n-300x122.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"163\" /> Leo District 306 A2 Conference - 2016[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1414\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1414 uomimage\" src=\"http://www.uomleos.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2016_multiple_conf-300x207.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"276\" /> Most Outstanding University Leo Club Winning Stage (Leo Multiple District 306 Conference) - 2016[/caption]\r\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" style=\"color: #0b93c4; font-size: 30px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  <strong>2017</strong></h3>\r\nUoM Leos were awarded for being the most outstanding University Leo club of the Leo Multiple district 306 – Sri Lanka, Under the Leadership of Leo Shehan Akmeemana, from PMDP Leo Rajitha Abeygunasekara.', 'Journey Towards Excellence', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1368-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-02 15:52:35', '2018-01-02 10:22:35', '', 1368, 'http://www.uomleos.org/2018/01/02/1368-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
